Data Visualization
- can track progress

Simple Personal Monthly Budget
Types of Budgeting:
1. Traditional
    - List all of your expected monthly expenses and subtract your expenses
to either your expected monthly income or balance.

2. 50/30/20
    - 50% needs, 30% wants, 20% savings/paying off debt

General Features
Account
[1] Sign in (log-in, create)
[2] Deposit money
[3] Check balance
[4] Withdraw money

Budget
[1] Store monthly expenses (add, remove, clear)
[2] Save money
[3] Display total expenses (wants, needs)
[4] Display monthly budget (using balance, using income)